plot: The two girls make a video with a goofy character that becomes a little too popular with the preschool set.

When Paige and Frankie realize that the most popular videos on the internet don't require much thought, they decide to make a silly video of their own about a moose named "Moosetashio." The trouble is, this new video of theirs has excessive appeal to kids under eight, who aren't exactly their intended audience. The real calamity starts when they try to get rid of their beloved character.—Daniel Timothy Dey
